<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Rit geannuleerd - <%= trip_id %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0682ca;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      max-height: 60px;
      max-width: 200px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #0682ca;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    td {
      padding: 8px 5px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    td:first-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 40%;
      color: #444;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #007BFF;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer strong {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 5px;
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <img src="<%= companyLogoUrl %>" alt="<%= companyName %>">
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Uw rit is geannuleerd: #<%= trip_id %></h2>

      <p>Beste <strong><%= customerName %></strong>,</p>

      <p>
        Helaas is uw rit geannuleerd.  
        Indien u meerdere ritten heeft geboekt, controleer dan de ritnummers in uw bevestigingsmails.  
        Heeft u vragen, neem dan gerust contact met ons op via  
        <a href="mailto:<%= companyEmail %>"><%= companyEmail %></a>  
        of bel ons op <%= companyPhone %>.
      </p>

      <!-- Ride details -->
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>Ophaaltijd:</td>
          <td><%= pickupTime %> (Tijdzone: <%= TimeZoneId %>)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Vertrek locatie:</td>
          <td><%= departure %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Aankomst locatie:</td>
          <td><%= arrival %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Type auto:</td>
          <td><%= carType %> - <%= passengerCount %> passagiers</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Uw ritprijs:</td>
          <td>€<%= fare %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Betaalmethode:</td>
          <td><%= paymentOption %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Klantnaam:</td>
          <td><%= customerName %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Telefoonnummer:</td>
          <td><%= customerPhone %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>E-mailadres:</td>
          <td><%= customerEmail %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Opmerking voor chauffeur:</td>
          <td><%= driverRemark || "N.v.t." %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p>
        Deze aanvraag is geregistreerd onder telefoonnummer: <strong><%= customerPhone %></strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <%= companyName %><br>
      <%= companyAddress %><br>
      Telefoon: <%= companyPhone %> · E-mail: <a href="mailto:<%= companyEmail %>"><%= companyEmail %></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
